            "body": "In the above lua snippet i set a lang map and a mapping.\r\nFor each combination in the langmap , first letter gets interpreted by neovim as the second one.\r\nThis behaviour does not apply to kemaps thought.\r\nThe above keymap works as expected using English characters but not when using the type set in the langmap \r\n\r\nI would expect that since i specified this \"translation\" in the langmap it would apply to the mappings set by the user.\r\n\r\nTldr:\r\nLangmap does not apply to keys in custom mappings",
